events.text: Welcome to your new league!
The Wizards traded Gilbert Arenas to the Grizzlies for a 2010 1st round pick (MEM) and a 2013 2nd round pick (MEM).
The Rockets traded Trevor Ariza, Aaron Brooks, Chase Budinger, Luis Scola, a 2010 1st round pick (HOU), and a 2014 1st round pick (HOU) to the Hornets for Chris Paul.
The Rockets traded Brian Cook, Yao Ming, a 2010 2nd round pick (HOU), a 2011 2nd round pick (HOU), and a 2012 1st round pick (HOU) to the Timberwolves for Corey Brewer and Al Jefferson.

The Hawks traded Al Horford to the Thunder for Shaun Livingston, Byron Mullens, Kevin Ollie, a 2010 1st round pick (OKC), a 2010 2nd round pick (OKC), a 2011 1st round pick (OKC), and a 2011 2nd round pick (OKC).
The Thunder traded Etan Thomas, a 2012 2nd round pick (OKC), a 2013 2nd round pick (OKC), and a 2014 2nd round pick (OKC) to the Wizards for Antawn Jamison and Mike Miller.

The Kings traded Francisco Garcia and Kevin Martin to the Bucks for Luc Mbah a Moute, Michael Redd, a 2010 1st round pick (MIL), a 2010 2nd round pick (MIL), a 2011 2nd round pick (MIL), a 2012 1st round pick (MIL), and a 2012 2nd round pick (MIL).
The Cavaliers traded Anderson Varejao and Mo Williams to the Bucks for Charlie Bell, Luke Ridnour, and a 2014 1st round pick (MIL).

The Grizzlies traded DeMarre Carroll, Mike Conley, Rudy Gay, Trey Gilder, O.J. Mayo, Jamaal Tinsley, a 2011 1st round pick (MEM), a 2013 1st round pick (MEM), and a 2014 1st round pick (MEM) to the Cavaliers for LeBron James.
The Grizzlies traded nothing to the Cavaliers for Luke Ridnour.

The Grizzlies traded Darrell Arthur, Hamed Haddadi, Steven Hunter, Luke Ridnour, Hasheem Thabeet, Marcus Williams, a 2010 2nd round pick (MEM), a 2011 2nd round pick (MEM), a 2012 2nd round pick (MEM), and a 2014 2nd round pick (MEM) to the Pistons for Will Bynum, Austin Daye, Jonas Jerebko, Rodney Stuckey, Charlie Villanueva, and Ben Wallace.

The Hornets traded Trevor Ariza, Aaron Brooks, Chase Budinger, Luis Scola, Marcus Thornton, and David West to the Heat for Mario Chalmers, Jermaine O'Neal, a 2010 1st round pick (MIA), a 2011 1st round pick (MIA), and a 2013 2nd round pick (MIA).

The Heat traded Chase Budinger, Daequan Cook, Quentin Richardson, Dorell Wright, a 2010 2nd round pick (MIA), a 2011 2nd round pick (MIA), a 2012 2nd round pick (MIA), and a 2014 2nd round pick (MIA) to the Suns for Channing Frye and Steve Nash.
The Rockets traded Will Conroy, Joey Dorsey, Kyle Lowry, and Pops Mensah-Bonsu to the Raptors for Jarrett Jack.
The Bobcats traded Gerald Wallace to the Nuggets for Malik Allen, Renaldo Balkman, Anthony Carter, Joey Graham, Ty Lawson, Johan Petro, a 2010 1st round pick (DEN), and a 2010 2nd round pick (DEN).
The Nets traded Brook Lopez to the Knicks for Wilson Chandler, Toney Douglas, a 2013 1st round pick (NYK), and a 2014 2nd round pick (NYK).
The Raptors traded Chris Bosh, Hedo Turkoglu, and a 2014 2nd round pick (TOR) to the Grizzlies for Austin Daye, Jonas Jerebko, Zach Randolph, and Rodney Stuckey.
The Thunder traded Nick Collison and D.J. White to the Wizards for Brendan Haywood.
The Trailblazers traded Brandon Roy to the Thunder for a 2013 1st round pick (OKC) and a 2014 1st round pick (OKC).
The Thunder traded James Harden, Serge Ibaka, and Antawn Jamison to the Cavaliers for Zydrunas Ilgauskas, O.J. Mayo, and Jamaal Tinsley.

The Trailblazers traded LaMarcus Aldridge and Steve Blake to the Cavaliers for DeMarre Carroll, Daniel Gibson, Danny Green, Darnell Jackson, Jamario Moon, Leon Powe, a 2013 2nd round pick (CLE), a 2014 1st round pick (MEM), and a 2014 1st round pick (MIL).
The Timberwolves traded a 2012 1st round pick (HOU) to the Rockets for a 2011 1st round pick (HOU).

The Rockets traded Shane Battier, Al Jefferson, a 2012 2nd round pick (HOU), a 2013 1st round pick (HOU), a 2013 2nd round pick (HOU), and a 2014 2nd round pick (HOU) to the Suns for Amar'e Stoudemire.
